The paper discusses a new accelerator for machine learning inference that uses memristor crossbars and general-purpose execution units. This work is related to computer architecture (cs.AR), electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), systems and control (cs.SY), and software engineering (cs.SE).
